lctemp (1.0.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial release
  * CPU temperature monitoring for Intel and AMD processors
  * Core temperature display
  * CPU usage percentage
  * Max/Min usage tracking
  * Fan speed display (hardware dependent)
  * Battery power for laptops
  - System tray support (Beta - Cinnamon/KDE)
  * Dark and Light theme support
  * Turkish and English language support

